FBIS3-34918 "drnes032_n_94004" FBIS-NES-94-032 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Feb 1994 LEBANON U.S. Reportedly Ready To Supply Arms to Government NC1502161394 Beirut AL-'AHD in Arabic 4 Feb 94 p 9 NC1502161394 Beirut AL-'AHD Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Unattributed report: "Why"] [Text] According to informed sources, during his meetings with Lebanese officials, U.S. Ambassador Mark Hambley has expressed U.S. readiness to supply the Lebanese Army and the official security apparatus with new military equipment. The sources fear that there are wicked intentions behind the U.S. readiness.
